	<string name="faq_title">Welcome to BattStatt</string>
	<string name="faq_desc">BattStatt does not act as an application but as a widget.\n\nYou can access BattStatt by either doing a long press on your home screen, selecting Widget and add the BattStatt widget of your choice, or on your home screen press the Menu button > Add and then selecting Widget and selecting the BattStatt widget of your choice.\n\nPlease note that the Motorola Droid/Milestone apparently only reports its battery percentage in 10 intervals, so you might experience that BattStatt isn\'t as precise as you wish.</string>
